title: Dream Chronicles 2 The Eternal Maze - Hidden Object Puzzle (Requ
description:
Return to the wonderful world of Dream Chronicles in this 

eagerly-anticipated sequel. Faye, locked away by Lilith the Fairy Queen 

of Dreams, once again needs your help to navigate this brain-bending 

and beautiful world of puzzles. Discover the origins of the fairies, 

hunt for dream jewels, seek advice from the foliage, and find your way 

out of the Eternal Maze. An incredible journey that crosses the lines 

between reality and fantasy, humans and immortals, Dream Chronicles 2: 

The Eternal Maze is a unique puzzle challenge featuring adventure, 

mystery, and fun!
